description:
Non-material amendment of planning permission ref: P032682 dated 18/10/2004 for the: ‘Demolition of existing buildings and erection of a basement plus six storey building comprising a four storey main block with additional 2-storey curved roof providing for 24 x one bedroom and 10 x two bedroom self-contained flats and three ground/basement level A3 commercial premises’.  The non-material amendments are:
A]	Reconfiguration and alteration of internal flat layouts; 
B] 	Reduction of window frame height to front elevation from 2.2m to 2.1m;
C]	Inclusion of solid panels within horizontal slot window at roof level, together with projecting guttering extending the entire length of the window;
D]	Enlargement and alteration of residential entrances at ground floor level;
E]	Enlargement and redesign of entrance/lobby, refuse/cycle areas within both residential entrances;
F]	Enlargement and rearrangement of windows and redesign or balconies to rear elevation;
G]	Removal of windows at ground floor rear elevation and insertion of louvers; and
H]	Reconfiguration of ground and basement commercial unit layouts/cores/entrances, including a reduction in floor areas.
